    <thetext>Description of problem:
If SIGHUP is received while expanding tilda, bash may skip updating ~/.bash_history due to a race condition.

Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable):
bash-4.3.42-4

How reproducible:
Very rarely

Actual results:
bash does not update ~/.bash_history

Expected results:
bash should update ~/.bash_history

Additional info:

Upstream bug report: http://lists.gnu.org/archive/html/bug-bash/2016-04/msg00106.html

Patch: http://lists.gnu.org/archive/html/bug-bash/2016-04/msg00136.html</thetext>
